description:
Visual Studio 2012 updates are cumulative releases that include new features and fixes that were delivered in previous Visual Studio 2012 Updates.

The following technology improvements have been made in Visual Studio 2012.5:

  - Team Project Rename support for Local Workspaces

The following issues have been fixed in Visual Studio 2012.5:

  - In Source Control Explorer, a branch operation causes an error and is not completed.
author: Microsoft
